Package: ggret
Title: Visualisation of Tree-based Phylogenetic Networks 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:c( 
    person("Gerd", "Specht",  email = "gerdspecht1995@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Arthur", "Kocher", email = "arthur_kocher@eva.mpg.de", role = c("aut", "rth"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9499-6472")))
Description: Visualisation and annotation of Ancestral Recombination Graphs and other tree-based phylogenetic networks. It extends the functionality of 'ggtree' and 'ggplot2'.
